title: Saraswati SuperCluster
p1: Discovery:Saraswati supercluster was discovered by team of astrophysicists from the Inter-University Centre for Astronomy and Astrophysics and Indian Institute of Science Education and Research led by Joydeep Bagchi and colleagues in Pune, India. Our Ex-educator Shishir Sankhyan was part of team.
